list.abstract: STRONG是一个英语单词，有强壮的、强健的等意思。

《Strong》是美国歌手Sonna Rele演唱的歌曲。收录在2015年4月发行的专辑《シンデレラ オリジナル・サウンドトラッケ》中。 《灰姑娘》是迪士尼公司出品的剧情片，该影片由肯尼思·布拉纳执导，莉莉·詹姆斯、凯特·布兰切特、理查德·麦登等主演。 该影片改编自同名动画电影《灰姑娘》，剧情延续迪士尼经典动画的故事——灰姑娘母亲、父亲相继去世，继母和其女儿们对她百般折磨，但灰姑娘得到魔法相助，成为王子的意中人的故事。 《Strong》是本片的插曲，由Sonna Rele演唱，在本片结束后随着演员表播放。

yingyinNormal.en: You are stronger than you think.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你比你想的要强大。

yingyinNormal.en: If only there was some one big and strong to push George along. I'm big and strong. I can push George. What a good idea, Peppa.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要是有一个强壮的人能去推一推乔治他就能动起来了。我就非常的强壮。我可以去推乔治。这主意身不错，佩奇！

yingyinNormal.en: Where is my strong Ross Skywalker to come rescue me. There he is.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我那强壮的罗斯天行者，何时会来拯救我？他来了！

yingyinNormal.en: Look at George, Richard and Redmond on tricycle. Next coming is the strong Danny Dog.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看乔治，理查德和雷蒙德在骑三轮车！下一个来的是强壮的小狗丹尼。

yingyinNormal.en: Maybe it just needs someone big and strong like me. That does not sound right, either.
yingyinNormal.zh: 也许这个需要像我这样强壮的人来吹才行。这个声音还是不对。

yingyinNormal.en: Everyone who believes they're strong eventually comes up against someone that's stronger.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所有相信他们自己很强壮的人最终都会遭遇更强大的人。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm strong. I'll have a go. Stand back, everyone. Do be careful, Daddy Pig. You are no that fit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我很强壮。我想试试。你们都往后面退一点。小心点啊，猪爸爸。你没那么强壮的。

yingyinNormal.en: Technically, it's a Chinese knockoff called Happy Strong Swimsuit Lady. Then I take it back; it's a great party.
yingyinNormal.zh: 严格来说，那是个中国山寨版叫快乐强壮的泳衣女士。那我把话收回，这派对棒极了。

yingyinNormal.en: We're seeking young ladies who show great promise in the fields of mathematics and science, as well as strong physical abilities.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们在寻找在数学和科学领域有巨大发展前景的女生，同时要有强壮的体格。

yingyinNormal.en: No. "Rajqawee" means "strong little man" in, like, 40 Arabic countries. And "Buzkashi" is "goat hockey" in Central Asia. And "warlocks" I was hoping they would connect.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，Rajqawee表示强壮的小男人。40个阿拉伯国家的语言都这个意思。Buzkashi是高山足球？和术士... 恩..希望他们有什么关。

yingyinNormal.en: Because when families are strong, America is strong.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为只要家庭繁荣，美国就会繁荣。

yingyinNormal.en: You're strong enough for the task.
yingyinNormal.zh: 您能承受这份考验。

yingyinNormal.en: How strong will it be when it hits?
yingyinNormal.zh: 飓风登陆的话有多强？

yingyinNormal.en: Foreplay is not Steve's strong suit. Isn't it?
yingyinNormal.zh: 热身可不是史蒂夫的强项。对吗？

yingyinNormal.en: I wanna quit the gym. It's okay man, be strong.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要退出会员放心好了，要坚定。

yingyinNormal.en: The wind is strong enough to hold up Daddy Pig!
yingyinNormal.zh: 这风大的足够把猪爸爸刮起来了！

yingyinNormal.en: Dark forces, when it's strong it, almost has a smell.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当邪恶力量崛起时，几乎是可以闻到的。

yingyinNormal.en: Could you use some help? Volunteer. I'm young, I'm strong.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你需要帮手吗? 我报名，我又年青又强壮。

yingyinNormal.en: None taken. Although "repellent" is kind of a strong word.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我没在意，虽然“厌恶”这词儿有点重了。

yingyinNormal.en: General Braegher is a strong supporter of General Brockhart.
yingyinNormal.zh: 布雷格将军是布洛哈特将军的强烈支持者。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: v. 加强；巩固；使坚强；变强
n. 力；力量；实力；强点；强项；长处；人数；强度
adv. 强有力地；坚强地；强烈地；气味浓地

word_family.mean: adj. 强劲的；强有力的；强壮的；强固的；牢固的；坚牢的；浓烈的；浓重的；强变化的；强变格的

sense_info_list.en: holding an opinion or a belief very firmly and seriously; very powerful

examination_example.sentence: People can contribute experience or information to your thinking—all the things that would make the disagreement <highlight>stronger</highlight> or more valid.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 人们可以为你的思维贡献经验或信息——所有这些都会让分歧变得更强烈或更有根据。

examination_example.sentence: Have a <highlight>strong</highlight> sense of social responsibility.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有很强的社会责任感。

examination_example.sentence: Reveals a <highlight>strong</highlight> prejudice against urban areas.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 揭示了对城市地区的强烈偏见。

sense_info_list.zh: 有说服力的; 充分的

examination_example.sentence: There is a <highlight>strong</highlight> case that those who have been worst affected by industrial action should receive compensation for the disruption.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一个充分的理由是，那些受到工业行动影响最严重的人应该获得中断赔偿。

examination_example.sentence: The correlation between happiness and investment was particularly <highlight>strong</highlight> for younger firms.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 幸福与投资之间的相关性在较为年轻的公司尤为密切。

examination_example.sentence: The relationship was also <highlight>stronger</highlight> in places where happiness was spread more equally.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这种关系在幸福分布更均匀的地方也更密切。

examination_example.sentence: For instance, failure can help you discover how <highlight>strong</highlight> a person you are.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 例如，失败可以帮助你发现你是一个多么坚强的人。

examination_example.sentence: When our time of mourning is over, we press forward, <highlight>stronger</highlight> with a greater understanding and respect for life.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当我们哀悼的时间结束时，我们继续生活下去，更加坚强，也对生命有更多的理解和尊重。

examination_example.sentence: Only <highlight>strong</highlight> people prefer to smile and value their life instead of crying and complaining about something.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 只有坚强的人更喜欢微笑，更珍惜自己的生命，而不是哭着抱怨什么。

sense_info_list.en: having a lot of power or influence

examination_example.sentence: What we decide to collect today, what we decide to preserve will have a <highlight>strong</highlight> impact on how we'll be seen.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们今天决定收集的，我们决定保存的一切，都将对人们如何看待我们产生重大影响。

examination_example.sentence: Yet it is principally during this period of <highlight>stronger</highlight> governance that CEO pay has been high and rising.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，主要是在这个更有力的治理时期，首席执行官的薪酬一直居高不下且不断上升。

examination_example.sentence: Most people do not realise that there are <highlight>strong</highlight> commercial agendas at work to keep them in passive consumption mode.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 大多数人没有意识到有强大的商业议程在起作用，让他们处于被动消费模式。

sense_info_list.en: (of a natural or physical force) having great power; having a powerful effect on the body or mind

examination_example.sentence: Nature's poll findings suggest that this trend is as <highlight>strong</highlight> as ever.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 《自然》杂志的民意调查结果表明，这种趋势一如既往地强烈。

examination_example.sentence: The new research reveals that the need to know is so <highlight>strong</highlight> that people will seek to satisfy their curiosity.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 新的研究表明，人们对知识的需求如此强烈，以至于他们会寻求满足自己的好奇心。

examination_example.sentence: Yet officials also hope for a much larger benefit: more long-term decisionmaking, to build a <highlight>stronger</highlight> economy for future generations.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，官员们也希望获得更大的利益：更多的长期决策，为子孙后代建设更强大的经济。

examination_example.sentence: Consistency is the key to getting <highlight>stronger</highlight> and building endurance and stamina.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 坚持不懈是变得更强壮、培养体力和耐力的关键。

examination_example.sentence: The 2019 study on dark patterns is mentioned to show their <highlight>strong</highlight> presence.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 2019年关于黑暗模式的研究表明了它们的存在。

word_usage.usage:
healthy，sound，strong的区别：
healthy指身体无病同时也可指身心健全、正常的。
sound只侧重身体各部分或器官没有病，无任何缺陷。
strong既指体格健壮，又指体力或精神上的力量。

examination_example.sentence: There was a remarkably <highlight>strong</highlight> correlation between how helpful supervisors were perceived to be and how likely their employees were to follow their directors.

examination_example.sentence: The link found in the new study was not as <highlight>strong</highlight> when they factored in the effects of certain health behaviors.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当他们考虑到某些健康行为的影响时，在新的研究中发现的联系不是很强。

examination_example.sentence: They lack a <highlight>strong</highlight> sense of self-worth.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们缺乏强烈的自我价值感。

examination_example.sentence: All these effects held true for measures of happiness, life satisfaction and self-esteem, with the effects <highlight>stronger</highlight> in the 8th and 10th-graders.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 所有这些影响对于衡量幸福感，生活满意度和自尊心都适用，在8年级和10年级的学生中更强。

examination_example.sentence: Rum, a <highlight>strong</highlight> alcoholic drink, which is distilled from sugar cane, is also an export.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 朗姆酒是一种烈性酒精饮料，由甘蔗蒸馏而成，也是一种出口产品。

examination_example.sentence: Managers usually love people who can self-sustain and enable growth through taking initiative, and who are <highlight>strong</highlight> at following through their work.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 经理们通常喜欢那些能够自我维持并通过主动出击实现增长的人，以及那些善于贯彻执行工作的人。

examination_example.sentence: They are born with a <highlight>stronger</highlight> ability to socialize.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们天生就有更强的社交能力。

examination_example.sentence: Now a new study has provided another contribution to the debate, uncovering <highlight>strong</highlight> evidence.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 现在，一项新的研究又为这场争论提供了新的贡献，发现了强有力的证据。

examination_example.sentence: They have <highlight>strong</highlight> negative emotions towards math.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们对数学有强烈的负面情绪。

examination_example.sentence: It faces <highlight>strong</highlight> opposition from many villagers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它遭到许多村民的强烈反对。

examination_example.sentence: It had already taken <highlight>strong</highlight> action.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它已经采取了强有力的行动。

examination_example.sentence: A poisonous fish which has a sting <highlight>strong</highlight> enough to kill a human is invading the Mediterranean, warn scientists.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 科学家警告说，一种毒刺足以杀死人的有毒鱼正在入侵地中海。

sense_info_list.en: not easy to injure; overcome; or resist

examination_example.sentence: Many people believe that passion and commitment are the foundations of <highlight>strong</highlight> romantic relationships.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 许多人认为激情和承诺是使恋爱关系牢固的基础。

sense_info_list.zh: 强壮有力的; 健康的

examination_example.sentence: Most of them have average to <highlight>strong</highlight> math ability.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们中的大多数人都有从一般到很强的数学能力。

examination_example.sentence: There are already examples of innovative schools which combine mental health and wellbeing provision with a <highlight>strong</highlight> academic curriculum.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 已经有一些创新学校的例子，它们将心理健康、福利提供与有力的学术课程结合起来。

sense_info_list.en: very powerful and difficult for people to fight against or defeat

examination_example.sentence: What doesn't kill you makes you <highlight>stronger</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 摧毁不了你的东西会让你更强大。

examination_example.sentence: But we believed in each other and our faith made us <highlight>strong</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但我们彼此信任，我们的信仰使我们变得强大。

examination_example.sentence: "Having a <highlight>strong</highlight> point of view, signature style, or being a super-enthusiast in a particular field makes someone interesting," she says.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 她说：“拥有强烈的观点、标志性的风格，或者是某个特定领域的超级爱好者，会让一个人变得有趣。”。

examination_example.sentence: Cuts to local authority budgets have resulted in a significant decline of these services, despite <highlight>strong</highlight> evidence of their effectiveness.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 地方当局预算的削减导致了这些服务的大幅下降，尽管有强有力的证据表明其有效性。

sense_info_list.en: having a great deal of power

examination_example.sentence_trans: 需要有强有力的经济激励措施，才能让企业在这里落户。
